title: 4 Way Shell for 15A Anderson Connector (with Latch)
blurb: These are the high impact and corrosion-resistant black thermoplastic outer shells with a 4 way 15A Anderson® multi-connectors. They allow easy connection and disconnection for the electrical equipment in commercial and industrial applications. The cable clamps provides strain relief and integral latches to prevent any accidental disconnections of your equipment. The positive latching provides security in applications where shock or vibration may be severe and the integral strain relief to reduce the risk of wire breakage.
